1. *Čeka* se na autobus. (He is waiting for the bus.) 
2. Ona *čeka* da završi školu. (She is waiting to finish school.)
3. Oni su *čekali* da stignu na vreme. (They were waiting to arrive in time.)
4. Oni su *čekali* da govor bude završen. (They were waiting for the speech to finish.)
5. Ja *čekam* da vidim šta će se desiti. (I am waiting to see what will happen.)
6. Njegovi roditelji *čekaju* da se vrate kući. (His parents are waiting to come back home.)
7. Ona je *čekala* da se smiri. (She was waiting to calm down.)
8. Mi *čekamo* da se situacija promeni. (We are waiting for the situation to change.)